
   ABILITY:  blackmail <player>
   LEVEL:    Wiseguy
   COST:     Low graft

   DESCRIPTION:
     This ability is a combination of protect and intimidate
     with a much more powerful result.  You'll have to try it
     to see for yourself, but beware - it can't be used very
     often.
     NOTE: Players that have paid protection will not be
     affected by this ability.  See 'mhelp protect'.

